    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pose in Asian art and dance comprising a standing body position characterized by three-bends, often with the weight on one leg, tilted head, and the body curved in opposite directions at the waist and neck to form an "S" shape.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
